{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bec6706a9f","title":"励志联叫","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dba1ca3e59","index":0,"year":1938,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"bec6706a9f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2ce4f98391","type":"paragraph","text":"励志联叫（1938年）失败者成功之母，","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"bec6706a9f"},{"id":"4e030fc1bd","type":"paragraph","text":"因难者胜利之基！1]1937年10月25日，毛泽东和英国记者见特兰谈话。当见特兰问“如何克服投降主义”时，毛泽东说：“言论上指出投降主义的危险，行动上之号，从失败经验中取得了费训，即是将来胜利的基础。恶观主义只看见抗战中的失败，不看见抗战中的成绩，尤其不着见失败中已经包含了胜利的因素，我们应当向人民指出战争的胜利前途，使他们明白失败和因难的暂时段话的精神的高度概据，为鼓舞念国军民李政抗战胜利而作。生海战成的司，用环时信补吃！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"bec6706a9f"}],"page":{"id":"a2ec359094","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"bec6706a9f","start":105,"end":106}}}},"__N_SSG":true}